#: C/gtkmm-tutorial-in.xml:8336(para)
msgid ""
"For instance, to create a signal that sends 2 parameters, a <type>bool</"
"type> and an <type>int</type>, just declare a <classname>sigc::signal</"
"classname>, like so: <placeholder-1/>"
